reviewText: Our family loves Taylor, but this DVD was pretty boring. Interviews back to back that said a lot of the same things. It was cute seeing her at different ages, but we fast forwarded it a lot and can't imagine watching it again.
A COMPILATION OF LOTS OF HER INTERVIEWS ON DIFFERENT TV STATIONS. SOME NOT VERY GOOD RECORDINGS. LOST INTEREST WATCHING...
Maybe it is just me, but how can you rate any Taylor Swift produce any way but splindifference.
Great DVD for any Taylor fan. It contains old & recent interviews. Very well done. Highly recommend!

This DVD was very well done and portrays Taylor Swift as the wholesome down to earth person she really is!!
I really liked this DVD.
